{"thag2.43:0.1":"Theragatha 2.43 ","thag2.43:0.2":"Dukanipata ","thag2.43:0.3":"Pancamavagga ","thag2.43:0.4":"Brahmalittheragatha ","thag2.43:1.1":"“Kassindriyani samathangatani, ","thag2.43:1.2":"Assa yatha sarathina sudanta; ","thag2.43:1.3":"Pahinamanassa anasavassa, ","thag2.43:1.4":"Devapi kassa pihayanti tadinoti. ","thag2.43:2.1":"Mayhindriyani samathangatani, ","thag2.43:2.2":"Assa yatha sarathina sudanta; ","thag2.43:2.3":"Pahinamanassa anasavassa, ","thag2.43:2.4":"Devapi mayham pihayanti tadino”ti. ","thag2.43:2.5":"… Brahmali thero …. "}